          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/31602357-spunky-n-sassy?shelf=5-star">5-star</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/31602357-spunky-n-sassy?shelf=4-star">4-star</a>
