        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3151926339" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16744156940029438882">What can I say except this author always drags me kicking and screaming into a romance novel? Not because I don&apos;t like her writing, but because I&apos;m not a fan of romance stories. But every time I see a new book from her, I jump right in and there I go, liking a romance story. I can&apos;t help but think that those who truly enjoy a well-written romance with a touch of mystery set in amazing surroundings, would love this book. A modern story set in London with a trip to Romania, the home of this author</span>
  <span id="freeText16744156940029438882" style="display:none">What can I say except this author always drags me kicking and screaming into a romance novel? Not because I don't like her writing, but because I'm not a fan of romance stories. But every time I see a new book from her, I jump right in and there I go, liking a romance story. I can't help but think that those who truly enjoy a well-written romance with a touch of mystery set in amazing surroundings, would love this book. A modern story set in London with a trip to Romania, the home of this author. Well done, Melinda de Ross</span>
